Package: zztable1
Title: Create Publication-Ready Summary Tables for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("RG", "Thomas", , "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1686-4965"))
Description: Creates publication-ready tables summarizing baseline characteristics
    by treatment group for clinical trial data. Handles categorical and continuous
    variables, computes appropriate statistics, and formats results for publication.
